      "beast_baseline": "that makes sense. for the script, i want to show some of the conflict more clearly. do you think the tension usually comes from things like socioeconomic struggles or just the personality clashes? and like, would the noise and the food be different if the family was, say, more upper class vs working class? i'm trying to see if there are certain traits or \"vibes\" that define these households specifically.",
